    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎，OPRTR-B0T-3457！</strong></h2>你将负责执行星际采矿任务，提取外星行星的能量并带回INTERGALACTICORP。小心，这些外星行星很敌对，你需要使用蛮力才能在完成任务前生存下来。不要空手而归。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/bfb81526b7232f31cdbfa51dea7ed36d.poster.avif?t=1741020326\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/bfb81526b7232f31cdbfa51dea7ed36d.webm?t=1741020326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/bfb81526b7232f31cdbfa51dea7ed36d.mp4?t=1741020326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你的目标是钻到行星的核心，收集珍贵的矿石和资源，用于升级设备和在公司的商店购买新机器。但请注意，维护你的机器至关重要；它们可能会出现故障或需要维修。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>维护你的飞船</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/cb54b122e2d86a7e2902afeb86eeb269.poster.avif?t=1741020326\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/cb54b122e2d86a7e2902afeb86eeb269.webm?t=1741020326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/cb54b122e2d86a7e2902afeb86eeb269.mp4?t=1741020326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>始终优先考虑维护你的飞船。我们将其托付给你，不能容忍失败。效率是关键！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>小心故障</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/983f9c45d84301b2ce346859ef9a0983.poster.avif?t=1741020326\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/983f9c45d84301b2ce346859ef9a0983.webm?t=1741020326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/983f9c45d84301b2ce346859ef9a0983.mp4?t=1741020326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你的设备可能会发生故障。迅速修复任何问题，否则情况可能会变得混乱！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>防御敌对势力</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/a974ca1525a0942896fc4eecef9b6835.poster.avif?t=1741020326\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/a974ca1525a0942896fc4eecef9b6835.webm?t=1741020326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070720/extras/a974ca1525a0942896fc4eecef9b6835.mp4?t=1741020326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这些行星不会友好，提取资源并将其用于升级防御系统。利用多余的能量，发挥飞船武器的真正威力，击败强大的敌人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>公司中的声誉</strong></h2>你在任务中的表现对于你的公司声誉至关重要，决定你在排行榜中的排名。任务中的出色表现将解锁更好的装备和不同星系的任务。",
